<inglise> Other information may be obtained from alternative sources, including administrative records, provided that the data obtained are of equivalent quality. </inglise>
<eesti> Muud teavet v&otilde;ib ammutada teistest allikatest, sealhulgas haldusandmetest, tingimusel et saadud teave on samav&auml;&auml;rse kvaliteediga. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
